com.codename1.rad.models

Interface Property<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractProperty, BooleanProperty, DateProperty, DoubleProperty, EntityListProperty, EntityProperty, IntProperty, ListProperty, SimpleProperty, StringProperty

    public interface Property<T>

    An interface to be implemented by all properties of entities. Generally new Property types should extend AbstractProperty since it includes default implementations of the boiler plate stuff.
